org.jsmpp.bean
Enum BindType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<BindType>
      org.jsmpp.bean.BindType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BindType>
public enum BindType
extends java.lang.Enum<BindType>

Enum represent bind type of SMPP. There is 3 bind type provide by SMPP:

  • receiver (BIND_RX) - receive only
  • transmitter (BIND_TX) - transmit only
  • transceiver (BIND_TRX) - receive and transmit

1.0
